OL,3,CPolice hunt driver after pedestrian
OL,4,Ckilled in hit-and-run
OL,6,FA pedestrian has died after being hit
OL,7,Fby a car which failed to stop in
OL,8,FBirmingham.
OL,10,FShaun Harron, 44, was killed just
OL,11,Fafter 12.30am today (Sunday 26 April),
OL,12,Fafter being hit by a brown Vauxhall
OL,13,FAstra.
OL,15,FIt happened at the junction of Romsley
OL,16,FRoad and Adams Hill in Bartley Green.
OL,18,FThe car did not stop after the
OL,19,Fcollision and drove away in the
OL,20,Fdirection of Jiggins Lane.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/3
