OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1777317067
OL,3,CPolice hunt driver after pedestrian
OL,4,Ckilled in hit-and-run
OL,6,FMr Harron was treated at the scene by
OL,7,Fparamedics before being taken to
OL,8,Fhospital, where he was later
OL,9,Fpronounced dead.
OL,11,FInvestigators are working to trace the
OL,12,Fcar which had the registration LV63
OL,13,FWHN - and identify the driver involved.
OL,15,FSgt Rich Evans from the Serious
OL,16,FCollision Investigation Unit, said:
OL,17,F"Tragically Shaun Harron has lost his
OL,18,Flife after being struck by a car which
OL,19,Fdid not then stop, and our thoughts
OL,20,Fare with his loved ones at this
OL,21,Fterrible time.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/3
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
